*1st-level SCHOOL*
___
- **Casting Time:** 1 bonus action
- **Range:** Self
- **Components:** V
- **Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute
---
[Effect while under the spell.]

[You can use an action to end the spell and cause X effect. Mildly more powerful than other spells of its level due to requiring two actions to activate.]

***At Higher Levels.***

\pagebreakNum

#### Seal of Command
*1st-level evocation*
___
- **Casting Time:** 1 bonus action
- **Range:** Self
- **Components:** V, S
- **Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute
---
[Your prayer empowers you with divine radiance.] Until the spell ends, your weapon attacks deal an extra 1d4 radiant damage on a hit.

You can use an action to end this spell, causing a creature you can see within 30 feet to take 3d4 radiant damage.

