#### Seal of the Martyr
*2nd-level evocation*
___
- **Casting Time:** 1 bonus action
- **Range:** Self
- **Components:** V, S
- **Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute
---
Until the spell ends, you can choose to deal an extra 2d8 radiant damage when you hit a creature with a weapon attack. Whenever you do, you lose 1d8 hit points.

You can use an action to end this spell, causing a creature you can see within 30 feet to take 6d8 radiant damage and you to lose 3d8 hit points.

